<cb:div type="xuzang-notes">
<head>卍續藏 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0280011" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0280011">真下別古本有舉前描真話五字</note>
<note n="0280012" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0280012">量字別古本作確</note>
<note n="0280013" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0280013">瀾下別古本有覺上座斯人也此一相見不干着一點佛法打破玄妙窩窟露出衲子胸襟法眼掉棒打月而累及傍僧使奥旨攸歸抑有憑矣二十九字</note>
<note n="0281001" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0281001">咦字別古本作也</note>
<note n="0281002" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0281002">品等十六字別古本在拈云下</note>
<note n="0281003" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0281003">人下有此一示眾大似猖狂罵座</note>
<note n="0281004" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0281004">麼下有各人提起布袋看七字</note>
<note n="0281005" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0281005">諱字別古本作晦</note>
<note n="0281006" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0281006">通下別古本有之神術也四字</note>
<note n="0281007" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0281007">提等六字在於人字下</note>
<note n="0281008" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0281008">一等六字作這裡便悟去也是</note>
<note n="0281009" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0281009">頭下有其麼諱處更須截斷始得十字</note>
<note n="0281010" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0281010">者等四字別古本作此段經文</note>
<note n="0281011" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0281011">人下有此段經文四字</note>
<note n="0281012" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0281012">華下別古本有向閙處刺頭五字</note>
<note n="0281013" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0281013">玳下有於穩處下脚五字</note>
<note n="0282001" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282001">祇等十三字作宗家謂大理既明如喪考妣行人於此當究心焉</note>
<note n="0282002" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282002">趙等四字別古本無</note>
<note n="0282003" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282003">水下有非趙州即投子非投子即趙州也如善變者各見數着之先應在臨機自然條妥要知二老落處麼三十八字</note>
<note n="0282004" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282004">但等七字無</note>
<note n="0282005" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282005">來下有十字街頭與汝相見八字</note>
<note n="0282006" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282006">方作昭</note>
<note n="0282007" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282007">首等四字在於兵字下</note>
<note n="0282008" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282008">佛字別古本作此</note>
<note n="0282009" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282009">雖等十三字在於云字下</note>
<note n="0282010" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282010">較等四字作匙挑不上也七個字如</note>
<note n="0282011" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282011">矣下有道人當慎諸五字</note>
<note n="0282012" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282012">事下別古本有從昔去問取九峯七字</note>
<note n="0282013" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282013">裏等十三字別古本作看得徹師姑元是女人做大丈夫誰不知友及問着則奈何不下何也祇回為容易記得出家難</note>
<note n="0282014" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282014">狸下別古本有靈山白毫相光照耀於今日也十二字</note>
<note n="0282015" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282015">師下有玄路旁提四字</note>
<note n="0282016" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282016">且等八字作要知翠巖意麼</note>
<note n="0282017" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282017">云下別古本有寰中天子塞外將軍大用繁興勾當不易十六字</note>
<note n="0282018" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282018">云下別古本有脚跟伶俐不沾泥水行藏舉止動目應心十六字</note>
<note n="0282019" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282019">須等八字在於認字下</note>
<note n="0282020" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0282020">曹等九字無</note>
<note n="0283001" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283001">云下別古本有諮窮玄境理絕涉求旨預象先機非行造唯法眼匠心獨妙也二十四字</note>
<note n="0283002" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283002">起下有撥不開攪不聚六字</note>
<note n="0283003" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283003">不等三十八字別古本作肯也若泛汛舸非也如登峻仞瑞巖依稀越國彷彿揚州巖頭變化鯤鯨不勞神用乃宗門之緒餘也</note>
<note n="0283004" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283004">云下別古本有二大師一有多種二無兩般慣向枯木上糝花寒岩中發<g ref="#CB08504">𦦨</g>貴在棒頭開眼也三十字</note>
<note n="0283005" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283005">者等五字作如鐵鑄</note>
<note n="0283006" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283006">底等三字作的博山與他結一同參</note>
<note n="0283007" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283007">索下別古本有渠儂二字</note>
<note n="0283008" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283008">開下別古本有也則乾坤失色滄海瀝乾十字</note>
<note n="0283009" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283009">聚下有也則萬籟喧鳴六字</note>
<note n="0283010" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283010">且等十一字作人人一箇指頭他因甚這等會用</note>
<note n="0283011" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283011">視下有各見不同</note>
<note n="0284001" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284001">化下別古本有只具一隻眼五字</note>
<note n="0284002" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284002">且等十五字作半肯半不肯在溈山水牯牛依舊隨群逐隊也喚作句歸笑裏得麼君子耻之理長則就</note>
<note n="0284003" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284003">一等三字別古本作徹</note>
<note n="0284004" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284004">師下別古本有道字</note>
<note n="0284005" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284005">也等四字在於體字下</note>
<note n="0284006" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284006">庭等四字無</note>
<note n="0284007" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284007">大夫二字別古本作肇師論義莫不</note>
<note n="0284008" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284008">源下有混融依正通貫物情如不轉位就機盖是澄潭罷棹者亦何滯哉而二十六字</note>
<note n="0284009" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284009">正等十字作指花破夢大似駭鷄犀也</note>
<note n="0284010" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284010">師字別古本作魯</note>
<note n="0284011" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284011">拈云等一段別古本作藏有珠珠有藏藏珠易辨珠藏難知會此則破廛出經也昔東山索小釋迦傾出一栲栳何如南泉拋來擲去諸人面前無有不是之者</note>
<note n="0285001" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0285001">總等七字別古本作將謂一條白練去也裂破始得</note>
<note n="0285002" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0285002">博等六字別古本無</note>
<note n="0285003" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0285003">或等三十二字作破木杓間家具乃老翁恒常受用家私耳若論着塵塵三昧向七顛八倒處識取大師寂定法門斯具眼者也</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
